set_maximum

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_maximum -  Set the maximum number of message before they start being auto deleted when someone posts to the board.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_maximum(string board,
int max)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^board%^RESET%^ - the board to set the maximum for
%^BOLD%^max%^RESET%^ - the maximum number of messages
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
0 if it failed and 1 on success
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/board_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Set the maximum number of message before they start being auto deleted
when someone posts to the board.
.EP

